What you need to know:

In the 65th minute, coach Kimani introduced Owiti and Pater Nganga for Marvin Omondi and Odhiambo respectively.Leopards goalkeeper Ochan denied Sharks a chance to draw level in the 72nd minute after he punched wide Masaba's shot inside the box. The hosts did not find the back of the net from the resultant corner-kick.